              "rowId": 52,
              "keyParts": [
                52,
                "p2",
                "verse",
                "v9",
                "content"
              ],
              "value": "for the stranger sojourning among them, that anyone who killed a person without intent could flee there, so that he might not die by the hand of the avenger of blood, till he stood before the congregation."
            },
